{
  "stem": "11882.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was a privilege to go to the courtroom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to get-- well, with Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kempner in his own trial, which was a very long trial, I would go with him always.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Almost always-- sometimes he took one or two other people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But almost always, I would go with him because I had done this research with him, and I had done the documentation with him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I would sit there beside him as a helper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sometimes there would be another helper on his left-hand side, and we would help him in the trial-- go get this for me or I forgot that, can you remember or something like that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE] was in the trial very often, very often.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the later, very noble President Richard [NON-ENGLISH], the son of one of our defendants, was a few meters away from me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he's very kind, always very kind to Robert Kempner.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He understood this whole thing-- he had been a soldier, and he understood this and saw all these documents and realized what incrimination in their very often tragic and weak careers.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They knew better, they didn't want to do this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Shall I let my job go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shall I let Hitler get another Nazi into this?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They all thought of themselves as anti-Nazis, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the courtroom was a very interesting place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our trial, the one I worked mostly on, had, I think, 21 or 22 defendants.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were all ministerial-level government officials, and a few of them were admitted Nazi enthusiasts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And interesting-- their reactions and everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The sentences were very small in these trials, largely very small.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And unfortunately, as the Cold War developed, the German protests to protect them caused a lot of commutations or simpling of sentences.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
